{
  "entries": [
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "むかしむかし、きれいなおひめさまがいました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Once upon a time, there was a beautiful princess.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまは、きんのボールであそぶのがだいすきでした。",
      "prompt": "[cheerfully, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess loved to play with her golden ball.",
      "prompt": "[cheerfully, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ある日、お庭の深い池のそばで遊んでいると、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "One day, while playing by the deep pond in the garden,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "きんのボールがツルンと池の中に落ちてしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[dramatically, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "her golden ball slipped and fell into the water.",
      "prompt": "[dramatically, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「まあ！どうしよう！」おひめさまは泣いてしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[sadly, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Oh no! What shall I do?\" The princess started to cry.",
      "prompt": "[sadly, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "すると、池の中から変な声がしました。",
      "prompt": "[mysteriously, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Suddenly, a strange voice came from the pond.",
      "prompt": "[mysteriously, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「どうしたんだい？おひめさま。」",
      "prompt": "[curiously, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"What's wrong, princess?\"",
      "prompt": "[curiously, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "みると、そこには大きな、みどりいろの、かえるがいました。",
      "prompt": "[surprised, cautiously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Looking down, she saw a big, green frog.",
      "prompt": "[surprised, cautiously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「わたしの、きんのボールが、いけのなかに、おちちゃったの。」",
      "prompt": "[sadly, explaining]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"My golden ball fell into the pond.\"",
      "prompt": "[sadly, explaining]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるは言いました。「だいじょうぶ。ぼくがとってきてあげるよ。",
      "prompt": "[reassuringly, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The frog said, \"Don't worry. I will get it for you.",
      "prompt": "[reassuringly, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、ひとつ、やくそくしてほしいことがあるんだ。」",
      "prompt": "[seriously, inquiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But I want you to promise me something.\"",
      "prompt": "[seriously, inquiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「どんな、やくそく？」",
      "prompt": "[curiously, cautiously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"What promise?\"",
      "prompt": "[curiously, cautiously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「いっしょにごはんをたべたり、ねむるときはとなりにねむらせてほしいんだ。」",
      "prompt": "[earnestly, requesting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"I want to eat with you, and sleep beside you when you go to sleep.\"",
      "prompt": "[earnestly, requesting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまは、きんのボールがほしくてしかたなかったので、",
      "prompt": "[desperately, eagerly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess wanted her golden ball so badly,",
      "prompt": "[desperately, eagerly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「うん、やくそくするわ！」と言いました。",
      "prompt": "[relieved, agreeing]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text7_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "so she said, \"Yes, I promise!\"",
      "prompt": "[relieved, agreeing]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるは池の中に潜って、すぐにきんのボールを持って上がってきました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The frog dove into the pond and quickly returned with the golden ball.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまはボールを受け取ると、うれしくなって、",
      "prompt": "[joyfully, excitedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "When the princess received the ball, she was so happy",
      "prompt": "[joyfully, excitedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そのままお城に帰ってしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[hastily, forgetting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "that she ran back to the castle.",
      "prompt": "[hastily, forgetting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるのことをすっかり忘れてしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[forgetfully, carelessly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She completely forgot about the frog.",
      "prompt": "[forgetfully, carelessly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、その日の夕食のとき、ドン！ドン！と、",
      "prompt": "[suddenly, dramatically]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But that evening, at dinnertime, there was a loud knock, knock!",
      "prompt": "[suddenly, dramatically]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お城の大きなドアがたたかれました。",
      "prompt": "[loudly, insistently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The castle's big door was being knocked on.",
      "prompt": "[loudly, insistently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「だれだ？」王様がきくと、",
      "prompt": "[authoritatively, inquiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Who is it?\" the King asked.",
      "prompt": "[authoritatively, inquiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ドアのむこうから、「わたくしは池のかえるです。",
      "prompt": "[impatiently, demanding]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "From beyond the door, a voice said, \"I am the frog from the pond.",
      "prompt": "[impatiently, demanding]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまがわたくしに約束したことを忘れてしまったのです。」",
      "prompt": "[accusingly, sternly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess forgot what she promised me.\"",
      "prompt": "[accusingly, sternly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまは、かえるの声だとわかり、こわくて泣いてしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, crying]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess recognized the frog's voice and started crying in fear.",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, crying]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「いやだ！こわい！」",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, desperately]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"No! It's scary!\"",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, desperately]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、王様は言いました。「ふむ。約束は約束だ。",
      "prompt": "[thoughtfully, firmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But the King said, \"Hmm. A promise is a promise.",
      "prompt": "[thoughtfully, firmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるを中にいれてやらねばならない。」",
      "prompt": "[resolutely, firmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "We must let the frog in.\"",
      "prompt": "[resolutely, firmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "しかたなく、おひめさまはかえるをお城の中へ入れてやりました。",
      "prompt": "[reluctantly, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Reluctantly, the princess let the frog into the castle.",
      "prompt": "[reluctantly, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるはおひめさまのお皿からごはんを食べたり、",
      "prompt": "[shamelessly, expectantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The frog ate from the princess's plate,",
      "prompt": "[shamelessly, expectantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまのベッドのそばにねむったりしました。",
      "prompt": "[shamelessly, comfortably]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and slept beside her bed.",
      "prompt": "[shamelessly, comfortably]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまはかえるが嫌で嫌でしかたありませんでしたが、",
      "prompt": "[disgusted, enduring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess couldn't stand the frog,",
      "prompt": "[disgusted, enduring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お父さんの言うことを聞かなければなりませんでした。",
      "prompt": "[obediently, reluctantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "but she had to obey her father.",
      "prompt": "[obediently, reluctantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "眠る前に、おひめさまはもう我慢できなくて、",
      "prompt": "[frustrated, exasperated]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Before sleeping, the princess couldn't bear it any longer,",
      "prompt": "[frustrated, exasperated]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるを壁にたたきつけました。",
      "prompt": "[violently, angrily]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and threw the frog against the wall.",
      "prompt": "[violently, angrily]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「キャー！」",
      "prompt": "[screaming, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Aaaah!\"",
      "prompt": "[screaming, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ところが、かえるはたたきつけられたはずなのに、",
      "prompt": "[surprised, questioning]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "However, even though the frog was thrown against the wall,",
      "prompt": "[surprised, questioning]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "けがひとつありません。",
      "prompt": "[amazed, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "it wasn't hurt at all.",
      "prompt": "[amazed, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "すると、どうでしょう。かえるはたちまち姿を変えて、",
      "prompt": "[magically, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Then, what do you know? The frog suddenly changed its form,",
      "prompt": "[magically, suddenly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "なんと、かっこいい王子さまになったのです！",
      "prompt": "[amazed, excitedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and turned into a handsome prince!",
      "prompt": "[amazed, excitedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるの正体は、わるい魔女にかえられてしまった王子さまだったのです。",
      "prompt": "[revealingly, dramatically]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The frog's true identity was a prince, transformed by an evil witch.",
      "prompt": "[revealingly, dramatically]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまはびっくりしましたが、王子さまのやさしい心にひかれて、",
      "prompt": "[surprised, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The princess was surprised, but she was drawn to the prince's kind heart,",
      "prompt": "[surprised, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ふたりはむすばれて、しあわせにくらしましたとさ。",
      "prompt": "[happily, joyfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and the two were married and lived happily ever after.",
      "prompt": "[happily, joyfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "めでたし、めでたし。",
      "prompt": "[conclusively, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page10_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "And they lived happily ever after.",
      "prompt": "[conclusively, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまが池で落としてしまったものは何ですか？ きんのボール おもちゃの人形 えほん",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the princess drop into the pond? A golden ball A toy doll A picture book",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるがおひめさまにした約束はなんですか？ いっしょにごはんをたべ、となりにねむること お城の宝物をあげること かえるを友達として遊ぶこと",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the frog ask the princess to promise? To eat with him and sleep beside her To give him the castle's treasures To play with the frog as a friend",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまは、かえるが約束を破ったことに気づき、どうしましたか？ かえるを王様に紹介した かえるを中に入れず、ドアを閉めた かえるを城の中に入れた",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the princess do when she realized the frog kept its promise? She introduced the frog to the King She didn't let the frog in and closed the door She let the frog into the castle",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おひめさまが我慢できずに、かえるにしたことは何ですか？ かえるにキスをした かえるを壁にたたきつけた かえるに謝った",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the princess do when she couldn't stand the frog anymore? She kissed the frog She threw the frog against the wall She apologized to the frog",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かえるの本当の姿は何でしたか？ 魔女 王子さま 王様",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What was the frog's true form? A witch A prince A king",
      "prompt": "[inquiringly, calmly]"
    }
  ]
}